{"tid":1217064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(割席?) 中共外交部: 《逃犯條例》相關問題, 請你向香港政府詢問","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:56:45.000Z","uid":134071,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0e216280d068c7ad2bbba11f39bcc43cad364e","tid":1217064,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web//fyrbt_673021/t1671982.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2F%2Ffyrbt_673021%2Ft1671982.shtml&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=81b888f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web//fyrbt_673021/t1671982.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月13日外交部發言人耿爽主持例行記者會<br />\n2019-06-13<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n問：中方是否擔心如果香港抗議活動持續，立法會或許會在修例問題上作出一些調整？<br />\n<br />\n答：關於修例的問題，香港特區政府已多次對外作出了說明。據我了解，特區政府就修例工作廣泛聽取了社會各界意見，兩次調整了修例草案，對有關建議作出了積極回應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>至於下一步修例工作具體安排，建議你向特區政府詢問。</strong>我要強調的是，中國中央政府堅定支持香港特區政府推進修訂&ldquo;兩個條例&rdquo;的工作。"},{"pid":"125351174632d88e97818692fbc7b5f46d6e251c","tid":1217064,"uid":134071,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"美國《香港人權與民主法案》威力真係咁大?"},{"pid":"ce9080212140aff1987e365e9aae4a03a11a7958","tid":1217064,"uid":22553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"如果支國答香港問題，又會比人話支共控制香港，一國兩制已完。所以做下樣都要話唔關佢事"},{"pid":"8c77a342c10b5246a374df56670adf8107d5ea04","tid":1217064,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892dbb163f0e316e2911f0e09a7d0dd9a5a7402a","tid":1217064,"uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ce9080212140aff1987e365e9aae4a03a11a7958","tid":1217064,"uid":22553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"如果支國答香港問題，又會比人話支共控制香港，一國兩制已完。所以做下樣都要話唔關佢事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"之前中聯辦唔係咁講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>中聯辦主任王志民昨（14日）召開中聯辦領導班子會議，稱修例「既有法理依據又有現實迫切需要」，着香港各界要支持修例，「提升香港法治形象」。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦的會議認為，「安全是香港繁榮穩定的基本保障，法治和公義是香港的核心價值」，香港回歸以來，內地已向香港移交逾260名疑犯，惟香港與內地卻沒相關安排，香港應「落實基本法的應有之義」，盡快通過修例以及時懲治嚴重疑犯，為「受害者伸張正義」</em>"},{"pid":"05ba656809ccc6f1ea8a86141abad38f0f76498d","tid":1217064,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fdeb17d3d430bd486882300ab4f8ca8e513799","tid":1217064,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"075001857a2309e06c32ebaf88d28b40a970f897","tid":1217064,"uid":55913,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"美帝一話充公你d財產就咁？愛國呢？"},{"pid":"b4313c46e4ad4eee6ab5d9dafea12b00927349c3","tid":1217064,"uid":35191,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"美國一出聲 先有中共話唔撚關我事 係政府決定修例 <br />\n定為暴動罪又推落係班狗決定 開唔開會又推落梁君彥 個撚個唔想咩飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd0e09b3c43e2435b1af5d09b3a44388a4a0a78","tid":1217064,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4313c46e4ad4eee6ab5d9dafea12b00927349c3","tid":1217064,"uid":35191,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"美國一出聲 先有中共話唔撚關我事 係政府決定修例 <br />\n定為暴動罪又推落係班狗決定 開唔開會又推落梁君彥 個撚個唔想咩飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"互相推波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a18af1b272327051d7865235163f1b60dcf7654","tid":1217064,"uid":169074,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99f624